<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">秋季运动会</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525739466067094.png" title="1729525739466067094.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233712.png"/></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;体育，是力量的展现，是激情的燃烧，更是精神的传承。青春展风采，运动向未来。试问运动场上谁为天骄，且看我经管学子大展身手，欢聚一堂书写经管风采。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><strong>入场仪式</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 旌旗飘扬，乐声激昂，国旗护卫队手举耀眼夺目的五星红旗，拉开了本次运动会的序幕。一跑一跳，一投一掷，都在尽情展现着青春的活力和运动的魅力。也突显着江软学子们不断超越自我，无畏拼搏的少年意气。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525761126016624.png" title="1729525761126016624.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233719.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525780359089741.png" title="1729525780359089741.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233725.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525803072045882.png" title="1729525803072045882.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233732.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525825806056678.png" title="1729525825806056678.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233738.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">方阵入场</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 老师们和同学们以想象联结现实，以创意赋予动力，将班级特色文化融入方阵队列，展现出独一无二的风采。经管经管，勇往直前，赛场争锋，共创佳绩。一声声铿锵有力的口号回荡在操场上。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525843380033009.png" title="1729525843380033009.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233744.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525860488025185.png" title="1729525860488025185.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233750.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525889374074771.png" title="1729525889374074771.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233756.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241021/1729525913571007695.png" title="1729525913571007695.png" alt="微信图片_20241021233805.png"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在这个金秋送爽，硕果累累的季节里，我们齐聚一堂，共同迎来了我校一年一度的秋季运动会。经管学子们热情洋溢， 朝气蓬勃，为校园送上最别致的妆点。秋日跃动，青春飞扬。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 绿茵场上，我们挥洒青春的笔墨，红跑道上，我们书写青春的篇章。运动会，这不仅仅是一场体育竞技的集合，更是一次心灵的触动，一次精神的升华。</span></p><p><br/></p>